{"tid":1593535,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"李小龍故居遭清拆　影迷會斥政府「棄救」","createTime":"2019-09-25T06:09:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-25T06:42:43.000Z","uid":48083,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"9d60922d40cba8aa6687d834c21eb0822f12db95","tid":1593535,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T06:09:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/09/25/140849_0d0de5c6eb9c00db9376480980ca1377.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F09%2F25%2F140849_0d0de5c6eb9c00db9376480980ca1377.jpeg&h=eaf56ce2&s={SIZE}\" />一代武打巨星李小龍為香港流行文化傳奇人物，其金句「Be Water」的精神更延續至今。然而，位於九龍塘的李小龍故居卻傳出清拆的消息，影迷會「李小龍會」批評政府和業主「棄救」。就《立場》記者今日視察所見，李小龍故居建築已圍起，地上一片瓦礫。<br />\n<br />\n影迷會「李小龍會」昨日在 Facebook 發帖公布李小龍故居遭拆毀的消息，寫道：「李小龍故居於公歷2019年9月24日，在業主及特區政府的棄救下，於今日拆毀，一代巨星故居終作飛灰」，另附上日文版及英文版告示。今早，《立場》記者前往李小龍故居現場時，大門已被圍上，前園一片瓦礫，另已有工人帶同工具到場。<br />\n<br />\n李小龍故居「栖鶴小築」位於九龍塘金巴倫道41號，建於1970年代。1973年初，由嘉禾電影公司主席鄒文懷、小麒麟、胡奀家族和電影商黎姑娘等購入，租給李小龍一家。李小龍去世後，由富商余彭年在1974年9月，以85萬港元購入別墅，裝修後租作時鐘酒店之用，命名為「羅曼酒店」。<br />\n<br />\n直到今年7月，業主表示由於工程顧問研究報告指內部日久失修，修復開支龐大而決定拆卸，屋宇署亦於同年6月批出拆卸申請。消息傳出後，當時李小龍會隨即發起網上聯署，促請政府介入，將故居改建成李小龍博物館，既可成為一個新的旅遊景點，亦能保留港人集體回憶。惟政府至今未有出手幫忙，李小龍故居難逃拆遷命運。不少網民紛紛留言深表惋惜，寫道：「幾千億幾千億建造貪腐大白象，一個值得全球華人全球旅客朝聖之故居卻被放棄」、「一邊高喊旅遊業寒冬，一邊清拆一個世界級旅遊景點」等。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/culture/%E6%9D%8E%E5%B0%8F%E9%BE%8D%E6%95%85%E5%B1%85%E9%81%AD%E6%B8%85%E6%8B%86-%E5%BD%B1%E8%BF%B7%E6%9C%83%E6%96%A5%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C-%E6%A3%84%E6%95%91/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fculture%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E5%25B0%258F%25E9%25BE%258D%25E6%2595%2585%25E5%25B1%2585%25E9%2581%25AD%25E6%25B8%2585%25E6%258B%2586-%25E5%25BD%25B1%25E8%25BF%25B7%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25A5%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C-%25E6%25A3%2584%25E6%2595%2591%2F&d=ZBayvnjX3omFcj6xyood9OCrFKAYikA6kkEaryQCE%2B8%3D&h=c6576a19\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fculture%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E5%25B0%258F%25E9%25BE%258D%25E6%2595%2585%25E5%25B1%2585%25E9%2581%25AD%25E6%25B8%2585%25E6%258B%2586-%25E5%25BD%25B1%25E8%25BF%25B7%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25A5%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C-%25E6%25A3%2584%25E6%2595%2591%2F&h=d8bb7648\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/culture/%E6%9D%8E%E5%B0%8F%E9%BE%8D%E6%95%85%E5%B1%85%E9%81%AD%E6%B8%85%E6%8B%86-%E5%BD%B1%E8%BF%B7%E6%9C%83%E6%96%A5%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C-%E6%A3%84%E6%95%91/</a>"},{"pid":"eeb23995c909876739e27acbfa9c907aa0737564","tid":1593535,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T06:10:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/biFbOWs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbiFbOWs.png&h=404dfcfc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好撚癲，香港冇大台運動，已經發展到929全球冇大台反支運動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1592119\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1592119</a>"},{"pid":"fe7d58ae42655cb1d5b6ad5b6f807bbc1bc3784a","tid":1593535,"uid":269515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T06:11:09.000Z","msg":"個政府垃圾來<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">國&hearts;際&hearts;戰&hearts;線&hearts;需&hearts;要&hearts;你</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RH29z9Z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRH29z9Z.jpg&h=787fa8fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">☆</span>Tg channel 在此 <a href=\"https://t.me/twittermansyunzou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftwittermansyunzou&d=ZBayvnjX3omFcj6xyood9OCrFKAYikA6kkEaryQCE%2B8%3D&h=d2ff0e9d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/twittermansyunzou</a> <span style=\"color: gold;\">☆</span>"},{"pid":"46d999d4cd6c711c283d2d9cc7251e81ad21ca61","tid":1593535,"uid":191271,"li